<view class="page page-with-action recognition-input enter">
  <view class="page-title">识一杯</view>
  <view class="page-lead">知道酒名就写酒名；只看到配料，也可以只填配料。</view>

  <view class="search-illustration" aria-hidden="true">
    <image class="search-image" src="/assets/recognition-hero.png" mode="widthFix" />
  </view>

  <view class="input-section recognition-form">
    <label class="recognition-field">
      <text class="field-label">酒名 <text class="optional-mark">选填</text></text>
      <input class="text-input" value="{{drinkName}}" maxlength="80"
        placeholder="例如：尼格罗尼、Old Fashioned" placeholder-class="field-placeholder"
        bindinput="onNameInput" aria-label="酒名，选填" />
    </label>

    <label class="recognition-field">
      <text class="field-label">配料组合 <text class="optional-mark">选填</text></text>
      <textarea class="text-area recognition-area" value="{{ingredientsText}}" maxlength="500"
        placeholder="例如：威士忌、青柠、蜂蜜" placeholder-class="field-placeholder"
        auto-height="false" bindinput="onIngredientsInput" aria-label="配料组合，选填"></textarea>
    </label>
    <view wx:if="{{error}}" class="field-error">{{error}}</view>
  </view>

  <view class="quiet-notice recognition-notice">两项都填时，先按酒名解析；配料会作为补充信息。</view>
</view>

<view class="fixed-action">
  <button class="primary-button" loading="{{submitting}}" hover-class="button-hover" bindtap="submit">看看它的味道</button>
</view>
